# Diagrams Directory

This directory contains all visual diagrams for the MIT Networking Project submission.

## Contents:
- Diagram_1_PowerFlow.png - Power Flow Architecture (Energy Routing)
- Diagram_2_DailyLoadProfile.png - Daily Load Profile (Three Operational Scenarios)
- Diagram_3_BatterySOC.png - Battery State of Charge (5-Day Autonomy Scenarios)

## Usage:
All diagrams are exported at 300 DPI for PDF embedding.
